# WHY: force shell scripts to LF on every platform. CRLF line endings break the
# `#!/bin/bash` shebang inside the Linux container (`/bin/bash^M: bad interpreter`),
# so a Windows checkout that gets built into Docker would fail at startup. start.sh
# in particular must stay LF.
*.sh text eol=lf

# Let git normalize all other text files on commit; checkout uses the platform default.
* text=auto
